{
  "texts": [
    "In Appendix B.3 we show even chain-of-thought prompting also fails to defend REGTEXT.",
    "RQ5: Is REGTEXT ranking better than choosing random words?",
    "While Table 1 highlights that LMs are unable to learn from D train u, the isolated effect of choosing words using REGTEXT rank is not known.",
    "To evaluate the effectiveness of the words identified by REGTEXT, we compare them against a dataset generated by randomly selected words from the dataset vocabulary.",
    "We ensure that the random and REGTEXT identified words are both injected at the same locations using Algorithm 1."
  ]
